-- JPMorgan may raise bid for Bear Stearns
-- 
-- Mon Mar 24, 2008 7:43am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/03/24/us-bearstearns-jpmorgan-idUSN2431046920080324

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - JPMorgan Chase & Co is in talks to raise its bid for Bear Stearns Cos to about $10 a share, a person familiar with the situation told Reuters. 

 JPMorgan declined to comment. (Reporting by  Chris Reiter , editing by Mark Porter)